multiflexi-mserver (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * feat: add POHODA_TIMEOUT and POHODA_COMPRESS fields to credential prototype
    to cover all env vars read by vitexsoftware/pohoda-connector
  * feat: UI connection test now uses mServer\Client (pohoda-connector) so the
    check exercises the same auth path as the applications
  * feat: multiflexi-mserver-ui depends on php-vitexsoftware-pohoda-connector
  * chore: add vitexsoftware/pohoda-connector to composer.json require
  * chore: bump credential prototype version to 1.1.0

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Mon, 26 May 2026 16:00:00 +0200

multiflexi-mserver (1.2.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * fix: replace file_get_contents with curl in UI connection test
  * fix: add CURLOPT_CONNECTTIMEOUT=5 and CURLOPT_TIMEOUT=10 to handle
    frozen/unreachable mServer without hanging the web page
  * fix: humanize curl error codes (timeout, refused, unresolvable host,
    no response) into user-readable messages
  * fix: show warning when mServer responds with status=busy or processing>0

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Mon, 26 May 2026 14:00:00 +0200

